news.title: CAG slams TNUHDB delay in building houses under central scheme
news.para: The performance audit for the year ended March 31, 2021, tabled in the assembly, said against the total housing demand of 13.92 lakh, the TNUHDB obtained sanction for only 7.08 lakh houses during 2015-21.

news.title: Ahmedabad: Property tax leviable for paid parking
news.para: The policy says property tax won’t be levied on spaces in residential properties or commercial properties where parking is free.

news.title: NGT bars leasing of plot next to Navi Mumbai creek for development
news.para: Two applications, filed by the Navi Mumbai Environment Preservation Society (NMEPS) and a group of six city residents, sought that Cidco be stopped from going ahead with the auction. The base price had been fixed at Rs 1.4 lakh per sq m.

news.title: Property registrations up, Noida to add two more sub-registrar offices
news.para: “The revenue department has submitted a proposal to open two more sub-registrar offices in Greater Noida and Dadri. The objective behind this initiative is to alleviate the burden on existing offices and expedite property registration procedures,” Mishra said.

news.title: Act against SHO, court tells Gurugram police commissioner, calls officer 'incompetent'
news.para: The sessions court in 2022 dismissed a challenge against the trial and directed police in May to issue summons to the directors of Precision Realtors, Madeira Conbuild, Global Estate and Ireo Grace Realtech – all of which were involved in the project.

news.title: Check SRA potential at government colony in Bandra East: Maharashtra CM
news.para: Shinde added that after studying the site of the SRA in the government colony, its capacity and all technical aspects, including the funnel zone, a decision on redevelopment will be taken.

news.title: Supreme Court rejects bail plea of ex-promoter of AN Buidwell
news.para: A bench of justices Aniruddha Bose and Bela M Trivedi on October 4 dismissed the plea of Surendra Kumar Hooda, ex-promoters and directors of real estate company AN Buidwell.

news.title: Haryana government announces new policy to convert residential plots to commercial
news.para: The "Haryana Municipal Urban Built-Plan Reform Policy, 2023" was approved at a meeting of the state cabinet, which was presided over by Chief Minister Manohar Lal Khattar.

news.title: Kalyan-Dombivli civic body appoints special team for survey of dangerous structures
news.para: In a recent tragic incident in Dombivli city, one dangerous building collapsed, resulting in the loss of two lives and one person being injured.

news.title: Hero Realty forms JV with Saheb Enterprise for a residential project in Gurugram
news.para: This is the second joint venture by Hero realty with the same company. In April 2023, both the companies had entered into JV to develop an approximately 2 million square feet targeting revenue of Rs 2000 crore.

news.title: Noida: Skytech Colour Avenue alottee gets refund due to mediation of UP-RERA
news.para: Ajay Kumar Gupta had bought a unit in a project, Skytech Colour Avenue, being developed by Jatasya Promoters in Greater Noida West. The proposed date of possession was July 2019.

news.title: Bank of Baroda to raise Rs 10,000 crore to fund infra and affordable housing projects
news.para: The approval is for raising Long Term Bonds for Financing of Infrastructure and Affordable Housing aggregating to a total size of up to Rs 10,000 crore, in single or multiple tranches during 2023-24 and beyond, if found expedient, BoB said in a regulatory filing.

news.title: Andhra Pradesh CM to launch five lakh houses on October 12
news.para: House-warming celebrations in about 5 lakh houses — under the YSR Jagananna scheme — completed in different Jagananna colonies will be simultaneously held soon after the chief minister formally inaugurates the colony in Samalkot.

news.title: Goa: Delays in registering of sale deeds at sub-registrar office irk citizens
news.para: ​In fact, applicants complain that they are being made to pay for appointments at Panaji and Margao and have to wait for nearly a month to get copies of sale deeds.

news.title: Indore & Ujjain divisions collect Rs 1,993 crore revenue from property registrations
news.para: In the first six months of the 2023-24 financial year, 2,73,876 properties were registered across 15 districts falling under Indore and Ujjain divisions.

news.title: Chandigarh administration employees' new stance may end housing scheme deadlock
news.para: The CHB had received 7,811 applications for four categories of flats. On November 4, 2010, 3,930 applicants succeeded in getting the allotment in their favour in a draw of lots.

news.title: NCLAT sets aside order to restart sale of Viceroy Hotels
news.para: In June, the Hyderabad bench of the NCLT rejected a lender-approved plan, stating that the performance bank guarantee furnished by the successful resolution applicant, Anirudh Agro Farm, had expired.

news.title: Godrej Properties to sell 14 acres land in Gurugram
news.para: The Mumbai-based real estate company bought the land in Sector 89 around two years ago from a local land-aggregating company.

news.title: NSDL to acquire office space in BKC from IDFC Bank
news.para: “This property, located in Naman Chambers, will serve as NSDL's new headquarter, with a move-in date expected by January-February 2024 after a 4-month fit-out period,” people aware of the deal said.
